text: Márton Sipos (19 January 1900 - 11 December 1926) was a Hungarian swimmer. He competed in the men's 200 metre breaststroke event at the 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1900 births Category:1926 deaths Category:Hungarian male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Hungary Category:Swimmers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:People from Szekszárd Category:Male breaststroke swimmers
